Package: linux-headers-goldfish
Architecture: armhf
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-goldfish 
Description: Linux kernel headers for the goldfish kernel.
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for the goldfish kernel.

Package: linux-image-goldfish
Architecture: armhf
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-goldfish
Description: Linux kernel image for the goldfish kernel.
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for the goldfish kernel.

Package: linux-goldfish
Architecture: armhf
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-goldfish (= ${source:Version}), linux-headers-goldfish (= ${source:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel for the goldfish kernel.
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel available
 for the goldfish kernel.

